Dog-SEP

EDA

Radoslaw Panczak

08 June, 2021

dog_ownership_cost <- read_rds("data/permits/dog_ownership_cost.Rds") 

SSC <- read_rds("data/geo/SSC.Rds")

1 All Brisbane dogs combined

dog_ownership_cost %>% 
  mutate(expensive = as_factor(expensive)) %>% 
  mutate(dog_breed = fct_lump(dog_breed, n = 50)) %>%
  group_by(dog_breed) %>% 
  mutate(total = n()) %>% 
  group_by(dog_breed, expensive) %>% 
  summarise(count = n(),
            total = first(total)) %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x = reorder(dog_breed, total) , 
             y = count,
             fill = expensive)) + 
  geom_col() +
  coord_flip() +
  ylab("Number of dogs") + xlab("")

2 All dogs per capita

dog_ownership_agg <- dog_ownership_cost %>% 
  group_by(SSC_NAME16) %>% 
  summarise(dogs_total = n(),
            dogs_exp = sum(expensive))

SSC %<>% 
  left_join(dog_ownership_agg)

Areas with no URP/SEIFA but having (small amount of) dogs:

SSC %>% 
  st_drop_geometry() %>% 
  right_join(dog_ownership_agg) %>% 
  filter(is.na(SSC_CODE16)) %>% 
  select(SSC_NAME16, dogs_total)
##           SSC_NAME16 dogs_total
## 1         Eagle Farm          1
## 2 Enoggera Reservoir          3
## 3          Karawatha          6
## 4             Lytton          1

Area with low URP and no dogs at all:

SSC %>% 
  st_drop_geometry() %>% 
  left_join(dog_ownership_agg) %>% 
  filter(is.na(dogs_total)) %>% 
  select(SSC_NAME16, dogs_total, URP)
##      SSC_NAME16 dogs_total URP
## 1 England Creek         NA  33

Dogs per capita:

SSC %<>% 
  left_join(dog_ownership_agg) %>%
  filter(!is.na(dogs_total)) %>%
  mutate(dogs_percap = (dogs_total / URP)*1000,
         dogs_exp_prop = dogs_exp / dogs_total)

SSC %>% 
  st_drop_geometry() %>% 
  arrange(desc(dogs_percap)) %>% 
  select(SSC_NAME16, dogs_total, URP, dogs_percap) %>% 
  slice(1:10)
##        SSC_NAME16 dogs_total  URP dogs_percap
## 1    Nudgee Beach         72  263    273.7643
## 2    Mount Crosby        394 1832    215.0655
## 3         Anstead        278 1509    184.2280
## 4      Pullenvale        585 3179    184.0201
## 5           Kholo         70  396    176.7677
## 6         Pallara         88  511    172.2114
## 7        Chandler        244 1442    169.2094
## 8  Pinjarra Hills        102  606    168.3168
## 9    Upper Kedron        692 4180    165.5502
## 10   Karana Downs        625 3862    161.8332
tm_shape(SSC) +
  tm_bubbles(id = "SSC_NAME16", 
             size = "dogs_total", 
             col = "dogs_percap",
             palette = "-Spectral",
             border.col = NA)

3 Proportion of expensive dogs

SSC %>% 
  st_drop_geometry() %>% 
  arrange(desc(dogs_exp_prop)) %>% 
  select(SSC_NAME16, dogs_total, URP, dogs_exp_prop) %>% 
  slice(1:10)

tm_shape(SSC) +

             col = "dogs_exp_prop",

4 Association with SEIFA

4.1 IRSD

4.1.1 Recalculated

SSC %>% 
  st_drop_geometry() %>% 
  group_by(IRSD_d) %>% 
  summarize(mean = mean(dogs_exp_prop),
            median = median(dogs_exp_prop))
## # A tibble: 10 x 3
##    IRSD_d  mean median
##     <int> <dbl>  <dbl>

##  3      3 0.147  0.140
##  4      4 0.147  0.144
##  5      5 0.145  0.137

##  7      7 0.127  0.128
##  8      8 0.148  0.148
##  9      9 0.126  0.122
## 10     10 0.127  0.114
SSC %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x = as.factor(IRSD_d), 
             y = dogs_exp_prop)) + 
  geom_boxplot()
